# Internal analytics scripts stay private, BUT the supervised dev launcher under
# scripts/ ships (README/CONTRIBUTING document `bun run dev`). Ignore the dir's
# contents, then re-include the launcher files. (Cannot ignore `scripts/` wholesale
# and re-include children — git won't descend into a fully-ignored dir.)
scripts/*
!scripts/dev.ts
!scripts/lib/
!scripts/tsconfig.json
!scripts/verify-pack.mjs
report_kpi_33_sessions.md

